units lj
atom_style atomic
boundary p p p
lattice fcc 0.4
region box block 0 5 0 5 0 5
create_box 1 box
create_atoms 1 box
mass 1 1.0
velocity all create 1.0 87287 loop geom
pair_style dsmc 2.5 29894 0.1 1.0 10 10
pair_coeff * * 1.0
neighbor 0.3 bin
fix 1 all nve
timestep 0.005
thermo 5
thermo_style custom step temp epair etotal press
thermo_modify format float %20.15g
run 20
